videos.headline: OSU's interim coach hyped up on sidelines
videos.description: Beavers' interim coach, Cory Hall, ecstatic on sidelines after Stanford kicker Jet Toner misses field goal.

videos.headline: Beavers pull off trick play in first
videos.description: The Beavers' Darell Garretson throws it back to offensive tackle Fred Lauina, who runs the ball 8 yards to put Oregon State in scoring position.

videos.headline: Beavers with the first TD of game
videos.description: Darell Garretson runs up the middle and stretches out for the first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Hall discusses Beavers' defense
videos.description: Interim coach Cory Hall discusses his excitement, and how the Beavers's defense is limiting Stanford's offense.

videos.headline: Beavers' Tyner 18-yard TD extends lead
videos.description: Oregon State's Thomas Tyner is handed off the ball and reaches out for another Beavers' touchdown.

videos.headline: Stanford takes late lead on Arcega-Whiteside's TD
videos.description: With under 25 second to go, Keller Chryst finds JJ Arcega-Whiteside in the end zone for the 3-yard touchdown and Stanford takes the lead 15-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stanford's take late lead on Arcega-Whiteside's TD) 2017/10/26

videos.headline: Stanford's Smith makes great catch
videos.description: Keller Chryst finds Kaden Smith who makes a great catch with one-man coverage.

videos.headline: Shaw discusses Stanford's win
videos.description: David Shaw discusses how they did not play well despite the win, and how defense kept them in the game.

videos.headline: Stanford's Phillips talks about their offense
videos.description: Harrison Phillips discusses how the fumble recovery changed the pace of the game, and how they are going to approach the rest of the season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Stanford's Phillips talks about their offense) 2017/10/26

videos.headline: Phillips recovers Beaver fumble to set up game-winning TD
videos.description: Oregon State's Ryan Nall gets hit and fumbles the ball, and Stanford's Harrison Phillips recovers the ball for a crucial play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Phillips recovers Beaver fumble to set up game-winning TD) 2017/10/26

videos.headline: Stanford squeaks by Oregon State with late TD
videos.description: No. 20 Stanford avoids the upset as Keller Chryst finds JJ Arcega-Whiteside in the end zone with 20 seconds left to give the Cardinal a 15-14 win over the Beavers.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Stanford squeaks by Oregon State with late TD) 2017/10/26 ESHEET
